text: Jaime Elizabeth Pressly (born July 30, 1977) is an American model and actress. She played Joy Turner in NBC's sitcom My Name is Earl. She has also starred in numerous motion pictures. She was born July 30, 1977 in Kinston, North Carolina. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from North Carolina Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Models from North Carolina
